            schools, our programs are designed to equip students with essential
            knowledge and resources. Whether weâ€™re fostering open conversations
            about menstrual hygiene or championing oral health with tools for
            brighter smiles, these stories capture moments of connection,
            empowerment, and hope.
          </p>

          <p class='text-base text-gray-700 mb-4'>
            We invite you to immerse yourself in these accounts of change, draw
            inspiration from the resilience of our youth, and discover how you
            can contribute to this meaningful journey. Together, we can continue
            to write stories that inspire, uplift, and transform lives. Join us
            in making a lasting difference!
          </p>

          <div class='mt-6'>
            <img
              src='/img/team-min.jpg'
              alt='Team collaboration'
              class='rounded-lg w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>
        </main>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class='md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-4 mt-8 md:mt-0 space-y-6'>
          <div class='bg-gray-100 p-5 rounded-lg shadow'>
            <h5 class='text-lg font-semibold text-[#185a69] mb-2'>
